

Purpose
The system should streamline how staff request office supplies such as notepads, snacks, slippers, and stationery, and allow admins to manage these requests efficiently.
 User Roles
There are two types of users:
Admin
Staff (User)

Authentication
Include a login system (frontend only, no backend required)
Users can log in as either:
Admin@2026
Staff@2026
The initial password/pin: abc@123
Later user can set their new password 

Admin login should include a simple verification check (e.g., predefined credentials)
🧑‍💼 Admin Dashboard Features
View all inventory items
Add new items (name, category, quantity)
Edit and delete items and reduce the item or increase the idem 
View all requests submitted by staff
Approve or reject requests
Display request status (pending, approved, rejected)
Staff Dashboard Features
View available inventory items

Submit request for items (select item, quantity)

View status of submitted requests
🎨 UI/UX Requirements

Fully responsive design (mobile + desktop)

Use a dashboard layout (sidebar + main content area)

Clean and modern interface

Use basic styling (no external frameworks unless necessary)
⚙️ Technical Requirements

Must be a single HTML file

Include embedded CSS and JavaScript

Use JavaScript to simulate data (no backend/database)

Store data temporarily using arrays or local storage
📦 Output

Provide complete working code in one HTML file

Code should be well-structured and commented 
